reviewText: I was the Dominatrix who trained her! Like the other reviewer, I never got a copy so I've never even seen it yet! Dennis obviously isn't a Dominatrix but I'm not mentioned here but they went to my big dungeon studio on Sunset Blvd to shoot me training her. We did the performance at the Knitting Factory before it closed. I made sure to teach her that Domination is not just holding a whip. I made sure she knew how psychological it is as well as teaching her safety in play. I named her Mistress Mercy. I haven't seen this episode but I will have to get it now that I finally found it!
I had allot of fun shooting this.. I trained to a  rodeo clown so I could "be more of a freak" I'm pretty sure not many people applied for this role! I needed the money..
